Because of a continuous flow of questions about antivirus &amp; security software,
here's a Top 10 list of well known and reputed antivirus &amp; security software. 

The list below is based on popularity, and the number of users and downloads. 
However, it is not an official Top 10 list, and also there's no such thing 
as an official Top 10 list (or a &quot;the best of whatever it is&quot; list).

Making a choice all depends on your own wishes and needs, as always. 
In case you need it then take the time to read the torrent descriptions 
and comments, because they may help to make a decision.

All torrents below are clean and working, and have been tested by many TPB users 
by now. In some cases problems and solutions have been posted, so remember to 
read the torrent comments before reporting issues. Also don't forget to read 
the included Readme!.txt file and Install notes!.txt file. Report possible 
questions only at the torrent(s) in case.


Note that of some torrents there's an older and latest (newer) version. Also note
that the Internet Security software contains a firewall, and already contains the 
antivirus option. So install either the Internet Security or AntiVirus software,
but not both of the same company/publisher. In case of installing a second 
antivirus scanner just install the av scanner feature by custom install, because
the other features may conflict with already installed (full) Security Software.   


As said, the list below is not an official list. However, if there are any experts 
